\c 115 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 115\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Isa Jiraataaf Ulfina Kennuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Nuyiif miti, yaa Waaqayyo, nuyiif miti, gaarummaa kee fi amanamummaa keef jedhii, maqaan kee ulfina akka argatu godhi.
\m \bd 2\bd* Sabni lafa irraa, "Waaqayyo isaanii eessa jira?" jechuudhaaf maaliif karaa argatu?
\m \bd 3\bd* Waaqayyo keenya waaqa irra jira, waanuma isatti tolu in hojjeta.
\m \bd 4\bd* Waaqayyoliin isaanii warri tolfaman meetii dha, warqee dha, harka namaatiin hojjetamanis;
\m \bd 5\bd* afaan itti jira, garuu dubbachuu hin danda'an; iji itti jira, garuu arguu hin danda'an.
\m \bd 6\bd* gurri itti jira, garuu dhaga'uu hin danda'an; funyaan itti jira, garuu fuunfachuu hin danda'an.
\m \bd 7\bd* Harka isaaniitiin qaqqabachuu hin danda'an; miilla isaaniitiinis adeemuu hin danda'an, laagaa isaaniitiinis sagalee hin dhageessisan.
\m \bd 8\bd* Warri isaan tolchan, warri isaan amanatanis hundinuu akkuma isaanii ti.
\m \bd 9\bd* Yaa warra Israa'el, Waaqayyoon amanadhaa! Inni gargaarsa keessan, gaachana keessanis.
\m \bd 10\bd* Yaa mana Aaron, Waaqayyoon amanadhaa! Inni gargaarsa keessan, gaachana keessanis. 
\m \bd 11\bd* Isin warri Waaqayyoon sodaattan Waaqayyoon amanadhaa! Inni gargaarsa keessan, gaachana keessanis.
\m \bd 12\bd* Waaqayyo nu yaadateera, inni nu eebbisa; inni mana Israa'el in eebbisa, inni mana Aaron in eebbisa;
\m \bd 13\bd* inni warra Waaqayyoon sodaatan, warra xixinnaa, warra gurguddaas in eebbisa.
\m \bd 14\bd* Waaqayyo isin haa baay'isu, isin, ijoollee keessanis mana haa guuchisu.
\m \bd 15\bd* Waaqayyo isa waaqaa fi lafa uumeef, kan eebbifamtan in taatu!
\m \bd 16\bd* Bantiiwwan waaqaa kan Waaqayyoo ti, lafa garuu ilmaan namaatiif kenne.
\m \bd 17\bd* Warri du'oon, iddoo warra calluma jedhaniitti kan gad bu'an, Waaqayyoon jajachuu hin danda'an.
\m \bd 18\bd* Nuyi garuu ammaa jalqabnee hamma bara baraatti, maqaa Waaqayyoo in eebbifna. Waaqayyoon jajadhaa!
\b 
